Please come in.

30
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:53,600
Zeliang, this is...

31
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:55,800
Chairman Huo. Hi.

32
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:58,800
I'm Su Xieyi, Mr. Li's temporary assistant.

33
