386
00:29:50,219 --> 00:29:53,039
It's just a matter of how long you can resist it.

387
00:30:59,319 --> 00:31:00,340
 What?

388
00:31:00,340 --> 00:31:02,960
 Didn't you say a tree has its own memory?

389
00:31:02,960 --> 00:31:07,100
