423
00:33:58,340 --> 00:34:02,140
Xieyi, your plan isn't the priority.

424
00:34:02,140 --> 00:34:04,259
Your safety is.

425
00:34:04,259 --> 00:34:05,799
Don't worry.

426
00:34:05,799 --> 00:34:08,879
I know what to do next.

427
00:34:09,639 --> 00:34:11,260
Okay.

